        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer648377144" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16504083739388073110">Another 5 STAR MUST READ from one of my favorite authors!! ... I may not know how to write reviews, but I do know when a book has fabulous writing that keeps me turning pages, frustrated when I have to put the book down and tired the next morning from staying up too long the previous night until I forced myself to close the book &amp; turn out the lights :o ... I just read this within 24 hours and 5 different times where I could sit and read in quiet! ... &quot;A Thousand Lies&quot; is now in my top 10 favori</span>
  <span id="freeText16504083739388073110" style="display:none">Another 5 STAR MUST READ from one of my favorite authors!! ... I may not know how to write reviews, but I do know when a book has fabulous writing that keeps me turning pages, frustrated when I have to put the book down and tired the next morning from staying up too long the previous night until I forced myself to close the book &amp; turn out the lights :o ... I just read this within 24 hours and 5 different times where I could sit and read in quiet! ... "A Thousand Lies" is now in my top 10 favorite books of Ms. Sharon Sala (aka Dinah McCall) and I have read 95% of every book she has written except the newer YA stories... My only problem now is what book will I find to read next coz it will probably be a let down after reading this amazing book :o ... You won't be sorry buying this book or eBook &amp; will thank us reviewers (the majority who gave it 5 stars) once you have read it, too :)</span>
