        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1235405590" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1959931270660234273">Off the chart crazy good!<br/><br/> This story had me blown away from the first chapter and I could not stop reading it despite the fact that I was so repulsed by villain in this story. He was so complicated and evil that you just couldn&apos;t believe his wife kept going back, even though you understood and knew she would.<br/><br/>I have read so many books, that I can usually see where the story is leading, but enjoy a good story teller so I stick with it until the end. I didn&apos;t see these twists coming. It was thrilli</span>
  <span id="freeText1959931270660234273" style="display:none">Off the chart crazy good!<br /><br /> This story had me blown away from the first chapter and I could not stop reading it despite the fact that I was so repulsed by villain in this story. He was so complicated and evil that you just couldn't believe his wife kept going back, even though you understood and knew she would.<br /><br />I have read so many books, that I can usually see where the story is leading, but enjoy a good story teller so I stick with it until the end. I didn't see these twists coming. It was thrilling, suspenseful, scary. It had underworld villains, para-normal moments, voodoo, and heroes <br /><br />The end completely blew me away! I stood up and cheered!<br /><br />Outstanding story and by far Sharon Sala's greatest book.<br /><br /><br /></span>
